  "description": "Download VAIL and experience the #1, highest-rated VR shooter, with precision-crafted gunplay, stunning visuals, and a constantly expanding world of modes, maps, and community. \n\n \n\nEXTRACTION (FREE EARLY ACCESS)Descend into the depths of Reyn to extract encrypted data, technology, and resources while autonomous drones guard it like archangels.\n\nTRAINING GROUNDS (FREE-TO-PLAY)Engage in non-stop action on four free-to-play maps designed to improve skill with weapon pickups and loadout modifiers.\n\nSOCIAL HUB (FREE-TO-PLAY)Challenge others to intense 1v1 battles, get the best score in mini-golf, and unlock VAIL Combat or other rewards by extracting ORE shards from the quarry.\n\nVAIL COMBAT (DLC)Gain full access to VAIL's complete experience. Dominate in popular team-based and free-for-all game modes as you level up, unlock rewards, and top the leaderboards.\n\nCRITICALLY ACCLAIMED\n\nJoin the party!",
